EDIT

EDIT is a text-editor


---------------------------------------------------------

Usage example #1 :
EDIT C:\FDCONFIG.SYS


---------------------------------------------------------

Features:
* read/modify text files
*

Supported:
* 8086+

Not supported:
* Files over 64KB
* long filenames
*  

Requirements:
* Sufficient free diskspace to save a copy of the file due to overwriting bugs
*
